                    <p>Breaking boundaries in visual storytelling and cinematic mastery.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="neo-card">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--bold-orange);">Scientific Innovation</h3>
                    <p>Leading groundbreaking projects across tech and science fields.</p>
